    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >上班有些无聊？来钓鱼吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >桌面钓鱼（Fishing On My Desktop）是一款挂机钓鱼游戏，能够以悬浮按钮的形式在桌面上运行。无论你是在工作、学习、看电影、甚至是进行其他游戏，都可以同时享受钓鱼的乐趣！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263340/extras/a4671d6de90e3ad6c8ce989ad1f51dc7.webp?t=1750935885\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263340/extras/a4671d6de90e3ad6c8ce989ad1f51dc7.poster.avif?t=1750935885\" class=\"bb_img\" width=549 height=100 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富的钓鱼体验</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >轻松一点即可钓鱼，无需繁复操作</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在河流、湖泊、以及海洋中垂钓</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过100种鱼类（可供收藏）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各具特色的钓竿和鱼饵</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一些意外收获：螃蟹、珍珠蚌、水母、漂流瓶，甚至宝箱……</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263340/extras/dc5f6549ca51f29149a024062db14aca.webp?t=1750935885\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263340/extras/dc5f6549ca51f29149a024062db14aca.poster.avif?t=1750935885\" class=\"bb_img\" width=549 height=100 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >以及</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一只世界上最可爱的猫咪</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3位可攻略的NPC</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30+steam成就</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263340/extras/f2c87bc7e19c37e1f31f434be4f2a8d9.avif?t=1750935885\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263340/extras_big/f2c87bc7e19c37e1f31f434be4f2a8d9.avif?t=1750935885 width=800 height=333 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>快来体验桌面钓鱼的乐趣吧！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
